es gender equality The sport of climbing is relatively new to the Olympics - debuting at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9835015257878095, \"rank\": 0.008854246575428956, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}, {\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999815329377, \"rank\": 1.8467141172758455e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9894172031660797, \"rank\": 0.010684259864565913, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"The Olympics' fastest sport Olympics\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"climbing\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There, not to everyone's taste, a single event combined three disciplines: lead climbing, speed climbing and bouldering.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone's taste\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"a single event\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"three disciplines\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"climbing\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"speed climbing\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"bouldering\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, speed climbing has been made a separate event, in which competitors scramble side-by-side up a 15-meter wall.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"speed climbing\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"a separate event\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"side\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"a 15-meter wall\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lead climbing and bouldering are still combined, in an event based on point-scoring rather than speed.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lead climbing\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"bouldering\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"point-scoring\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bouldering takes place on walls no more than 4.5 meters high, without a rope.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bouldering\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"walls\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"a rope\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThe only special equipment you need is a pair of climbing shoes \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and now that it's an Olympic sport, the climbing community has a defined route to success.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only special equipment\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"climbing shoes\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\":