51, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"fun activities\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cIt's one of the charms of the Olympic Games that it puts lesser-known sports in the spotlight.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the charms\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"lesser-known sports\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2727}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Climbing is one of those, and the Games organizers \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 determined to unlock the youth potential for the future \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 are handing over the Olympic climbing center to the local area once the Games are over.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Climbing\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games organizers\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"the youth potential\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic climbing center\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"the local area\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-850614